@toc index

    Index - BAUD Rates


                            BAUD           CPSą         TIME˛

                             110             11         26:48
                             300             29         10:02
                            1200            117          2:29
                            2400            234          1:14
                            4800            468           :37
                            9600            937           :18
                           14400           1406           :12
                           19200           1875           :09
                           28800           2812           :06
                           57600           5625           :03
                          115200          11250           :02
                          230400          22500           :01
                          292800          28594           :01

            CPSą is the measure of characters transmitted per second.
            TIME˛ is HOURS:MINUTES required to download 1 megabyte.


                            V.21        300 BAUD

                            V.22        1200 BAUD

                            V.23        1200/75 BAUD

                            V.22BIS     2400 BAUD

                            V.32        9600 BAUD

